  "title": "Aurelius, Meditations §aur_05_xi: What is the use that now at this present I make of my soul?",
  "body": "What is the use that now at this present I make of my soul? Thus from time to time and upon all occasions thou must put this question to thyself; what is now that part of mine which they call the rational mistress part, employed about? Whose soul do I now properly possess? a child's? or a youth's? a woman's? or a tyrant's? some brute, or some wild beast's soul?",
